|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.NamespaceSecurity>|<span data-ttu-id="99903-109">-安全 (DACL) 使用的命名空间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="99903-109">-   The security (DACL) on the namespace used.</span></span>|  
